name: Exuberance No. 1
description:
Reach for the sky and extend upward to the heavens; Exuberance No. 1 creates cosmic kinetic energy. This captivating painting pulsates in the colors of scarlet, bubble gum, violets, and ultramarine. Exuberance No. 1 is a one-of-a-kind artistic collaboration that intertwines Tery Spataro's flower photographs together and the artificial intelligence of Playform.io to give life to this transfixing creation.

Exuberance No. 1 comes with a physical print on canvas 15.7"x15.7".
